d=57248223&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant</a></blockquote><br />\n司機玩完，支那臭鴨肯定有性病😂😂😂"},{"pid":"26036101774901b14b81cbfff7d164639d5787b9","tid":412730,"uid":102421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T08:06:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}